YUMMMMY! I made this recipe for a supper club and everyone loved it! I used vegetables instead of chicken and have since tried fish which is also delicious. I agree about adding more cilantro and lime juice to the slaw, but PLEASE do not add mayo instead of oil.

Rating: 3
Really good--the only change I made was to use crema (a Mexican table cream, a little like creme fraiche), since I live way out in the country and was out of American sour cream. Crema is not as tart or as thick--but is lower in calories. With all the spices, I couldn't tell the difference.

